

The little decisions we make in life can have a huge ass effect on our lives in general. For me going to get some pizza in the middle of the night wasn't such a good idea yet at the same time such a good one. If I hadn't left the house that night I would've still been with my family and friends but at the same time if I decided to stay at home that night I wouldn't have met my love, my life, my soul mate.

Chapter One will be posted a few minutes later!